RSA Encryption/Decryption

To build executable on *nix systems type:
 $ make Rsa-crypt

 1. Generate keys g <path_to_project>/rsa/public_key <path_to_project>/rsa/private_key

 2. Encrypt data e <path_to_project>/rsa/source_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/encrypted_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/public_key

 3. Decrypt data d <path_to_project>/rsa/encrypted_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/decrypted_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/private_key

 ./rsa g <path_to_project>/rsa/public_key <path_to_project>/rsa/private_key

 ./rsa e <path_to_project>/rsa/source_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/encrypted_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/public_key

 ./rsa d <path_to_project>/rsa/encrypted_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/decrypted_message.txt <path_to_project>/rsa/private_key
